\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serum - Chocolate Frosting\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serums. Review + swatches of the new donut-inspired tinted lip serums from Laneige.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/02/laneige-glaze-craze-tinted-polypeptide-lip-serum.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serum\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-Chocolate-Frosting.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e_____\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere are a few features of the serums that I’m a little iffy about – none of these are deal breakers for me, but several of you mentioned these in your DMs to me so I thought I’d point them out too. Texture can be a little thick if you apply too much product, but they are easy to blend out.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI’m undecided about the applicator they made for these balms. The \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3QmNp9T\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eGlaze Craze Lip Serums\u003c/a\u003e come with a cushiony donut-shaped applicator. It’s soft and squishy and I give Laneige five stars for innovation, but it can be cumbersome to use as it makes precise application challenging. Also the tip can get very messy and a little goopy over time with the product oozing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serum applicator\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serums. Review + swatches of the new donut-inspired tinted lip serums from Laneige.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/02/laneige-glaze-craze-tinted-polypeptide-lip-serum.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serum\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Langie-Glaze-Craze-Tinted-Lip-Serum-applicator.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere was one shade that seemed to settle and separate into my lip lines on bare lips (the Peach Glaze), but this can be fixed if I apply a lip liner underneath.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOverall I am happy with the purchase especially since the pigment level is exactly what I want in a tinted balm. I love that they’re not too sheer. A lot of you wanted to know how these compared to \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/418SZQk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eSummer Fridays Lip Butter Balms\u003c/a\u003e and I feel like they are very different. The Summer Fridays balms are a little thinner in texture with just a sheer hint of color while the Laneige serums is thicker and more opaque. If you like the concept of a tinted lip product that is hydrating but want something more budget-friendly, I also recommend checking out the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/41v9qth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003ee.l.f. Glow Reviver Lip Oils\u003c/a\u003e. While the formulas are not really the same, I have been a big fan of them for a tinted lip hydrator and I think they also have really great colors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI pulled some swatches to some other balms/oils and a few glosses to compare for color.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serum swatches vs Summer Fridays, Fenty, Elf, rhode\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serums. Review + swatches of the new donut-inspired tinted lip serums from Laneige.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/02/laneige-glaze-craze-tinted-polypeptide-lip-serum.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Laneige Glaze Craze Tinted Polypeptide Lip Serum\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Laneige-Lip-Serum-vs-SF-Rhode-Fenty.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAvailable now at \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3Qo7SLc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eSephora\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4i9s4MQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eKohl’s\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3EKss61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eLaneige\u003c/a\u003e. Have you tried these yet? What did you think?\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\u003c/article\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
